nodes.text: Magnate Imperium was a title of high ranking in organizations such as the Ben Diffle Fantanines, in which Kako and Roz Fantanine both held the title. Baron Administrator Lando Calrissian was briefly the Magnate Imperium of the Fantanine mining colony, but refused ownership of the facility upon learning that the Fantanines were exporting members of the native species.
